column5: <think>#Newline            <set name="question1">Are you having problem with someone?(Yes/No)?</set>#Newline            <set name="question2">Who is/are the person/s?</set>#Newline            <set name="question3">Can you describe the problem from someone's point of view who was not involved in it?</set>#Newline            <set name="question4">How do you describe this problem?</set>#Newline            <set name="question5">How does the other person describe it?</set>#Newline            <set name="question6">Why do you see the problem that way?</set>#Newline            <set name="question7">Why does the other person see the problem that way?</set>#Newline            <set name="question8">What/How do you feel about it?</set>#Newline            <set name="question9">What kind of thoughts did you have about it?</set>#Newline            <set name="question10">Thank you for your response#Comma type END to end session</set>#Newline            <set name="responses">Session Responses: </set>#Newline            <set name="qnum">1</set>#Newline    	</think>#Newline	    <srai>Activity1Loop</srai>
